ZH: 1. 我会跟随你的脚步去任何地方。
EN: I will follow your footsteps anywhere.
ZH: 2. 她决定跟随他去旅行。
EN: She decided to travel with him.
ZH: 3. 请大家跟随我一起走。
EN: Please follow me.
ZH: 4. 他的宠物狗总是跟随着他。
EN: His pet dog always follows him.
ZH: 5. 这位导游会带领我们跟随历史的脚步。
EN: This tour guide will lead us to follow the footsteps of history.
ZH: 6. 我们都跟随着音乐的节奏一起跳舞。
EN: We all dance together following the rhythm of the music.
ZH: 7. 老师要求学生们在教室内跟随规定的顺序进行活动。
EN: The teacher asks the students to carry out activities in the classroom following the prescribed order.
ZH: 8. 在人群中，我总是看见她跟随着她的朋友。
EN: In the crowd, I always see her following her friends.
ZH: 9. 请大家跟随节目表上的顺序排队入场。
EN: Please line up according to the order on the program schedule.
ZH: 10. 小孩们喜欢跟随领舞者一起做舞蹈动作。
EN: Children like to follow the lead dancer to do dance movements together.
ZH: 11. 作为一名儿童保姆，我的任务是跟随孩子们的日常时间表。
EN: As a babysitter, my task is to follow the children's daily schedule.
ZH: 12. 我们要学会跟随潮流，不要被时代抛在身后。
EN: We need to learn to follow trends and not get left behind by the times.
ZH: 13. 请你跟随我做这个瑜伽动作。
EN: Please follow me to do this yoga pose.
ZH: 14. 学生们应该跟随老师的指示认真学习。
EN: Students should follow the teacher's instructions and study diligently.
ZH: 15. 那个小狗一直跟随着他，从来不离开。
EN: That little dog always follows him and never leaves.
ZH: 16. 他擅长跟随感觉作曲，而不是按照乐谱演奏。
EN: He is good at composing based on feelings instead of playing according to sheet music.
ZH: 17. 请大家跟随团队的节奏一起行动。
EN: Please act in sync with the team's rhythm.
ZH: 18. 她总是跟随着时尚潮流来改变自己的服装风格。
EN: She always follows the fashion trends to change her clothing style.
ZH: 19. 我们要学会跟随自己的内心，去找到真正的幸福。
EN: We need to learn to follow our hearts to find true happiness.
ZH: 20. 欢迎大家跟随我一起探索这个美丽的城市。
EN: Welcome everyone to explore this beautiful city with me.
